  "3156020": {
    "name": "Gloomveil",
    "steam_appid": 3156020,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>Gloomveil is a game that requires attention, observation and patience.</i><br><i>Designed for players who love deep immersion and the joy of figuring things out for themselves.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/69a5907d1005dc648b6a33732664794e.poster.avif?t=1771878447\" width=780 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/69a5907d1005dc648b6a33732664794e.webm?t=1771878447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/69a5907d1005dc648b6a33732664794e.mp4?t=1771878447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The World is the protagonist</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a <strong>vast</strong>, <strong>interconnected </strong>world that doesn't revolve around you. Each corner hides <strong>secrets </strong>waiting to be uncovered. Create <strong>shortcuts </strong>and familiarize yourself with the land to stay on course</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/6507f9e18c382c67af9f7d15f6705ed7.poster.avif?t=1771878447\" width=780 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/6507f9e18c382c67af9f7d15f6705ed7.webm?t=1771878447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/6507f9e18c382c67af9f7d15f6705ed7.mp4?t=1771878447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Journey over destination</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Navigating</strong> the world isn't just a means to an end, it's the <strong>essence of the game play</strong>. Observe the creatures around you and move through their territory with <strong>caution</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/5ffb7e4a075b286853a762727da07d2b.poster.avif?t=1771878447\" width=780 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/5ffb7e4a075b286853a762727da07d2b.webm?t=1771878447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/5ffb7e4a075b286853a762727da07d2b.mp4?t=1771878447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat is optional</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes, in moments of haste or fear, you might feel compelled to use your <strong>weapon</strong>. It’s your <strong>choice</strong>, but be aware that this could lead to<strong> unforeseen consequences</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/cb2c5f58ca1312094611b988ab070393.poster.avif?t=1771878447\" width=780 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/cb2c5f58ca1312094611b988ab070393.webm?t=1771878447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/cb2c5f58ca1312094611b988ab070393.mp4?t=1771878447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Vast Interconnected World:</strong> Find hidden paths, enter caves, discover new areas and create shortcuts, all in a physically coherent world with no loading screens.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Optional Combat:</strong> The game focuses on movement, rather than heavy combat. The world is filled with creatures, some aggressive some peaceful, and how you engage with them is up to you. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mind-Mapping: </strong>Guidance is heavily based on the memorization of the environment, it’s components and the marks you place. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover Secrets:</strong> Secrets are discovered through subtle hints and thinking outside the box.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple Controls: </strong>The game emphasizes navigation over complex actions. It can be played with one hand using a keyboard, mouse, or either side of a gamepad.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Day-Night Events:</strong> Experience a day-night cycle with events that change based on the time of day. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minimal UI:</strong> Enjoy a clean, immersive experience with minimal UI and no distracting indicators.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local Co-op:</strong> Play with another friend in local cooperative mode.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/dd177a03be7438977b02de71e0e3df69.poster.avif?t=1771878447\" width=780 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/dd177a03be7438977b02de71e0e3df69.webm?t=1771878447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/dd177a03be7438977b02de71e0e3df69.mp4?t=1771878447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/0c7a3b621237b05f776bab7e22adcd13.avif?t=1771878447\" width=1560 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About us</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi! We are <strong>Ricotoni Games</strong>! A <strong>two-person team</strong> that make games out of their <strong>love</strong> for them. We are trying our best to make games that <strong>WE</strong> would love to play! So those games might <strong>not appeal to everyone</strong>. What we really want is to <strong>create worlds</strong> that <strong>make us feel</strong> the <strong>same feelings</strong> we used to feel when we played games <strong>as kids</strong>.<br><br><strong>Music</strong> by <strong>Christos Giannopoulos</strong></p>",
